{"tid":1989181,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦突然關機問題，求解決方法","createTime":"2020-04-25T17:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T10:11:08.000Z","uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35c30c46df719ca4265f23cf3b486e9b1d2f16a9","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"部機用左1年3個月左右<br />\n自己砌機，最近一個月用用下突機關機，連Power都開不到，要關上大電制再開返先開得著。<br />\n<br />\n開過機除塵無用，加上也不是太多塵<br />\n<br />\n用Software睇溫度，CPU,GPU,用緊一體水冷（冇漏水）平均溫度是35度左右，玩遊戲都是50-55度。<br />\n<br />\n具體情況如下：<br />\n<br />\n突然關機，開不著，關大制重開。<br />\n<br />\nBios 開著10-15分鐘都沒問題，試過load入windows就再死機，之後開唔返。<br />\n如果順利入到Windows，用到1-3小時不等又會突然關機<br />\n<br />\n請問各位師兄知道大約咩問題嗎？"},{"pid":"e9af0d3471d8992428d2b50e403e9572149cebbd","tid":1989181,"uid":99861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"似死火牛"},{"pid":"e7c107a60578ea038de8e898cb3022acc7ec1ea2","tid":1989181,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"換部新"},{"pid":"04e5bcf75b18712d2f943aa3a0a5ec724e216eb3","tid":1989181,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇吓硬件有沒鬆<br />\n睇吓mb 有沒爆電容<br />\n睇下chipset 有沒錯<br />\n拔左mb 舊電<br />\n更新bios"},{"pid":"78be36d24c1d039c0040716c46c6a9b0d255315f","tid":1989181,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"停係Bios 1個鐘試吓<br />\n<br />\n換隻 hdd 試吓"},{"pid":"e09b445953aec4fc4f44241ed3be4ca157f2e017","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e5bcf75b18712d2f943aa3a0a5ec724e216eb3","tid":1989181,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇吓硬件有沒鬆<br />\n睇吓mb 有沒爆電容<br />\n睇下chipset 有沒錯<br />\n拔左mb 舊電<br />\n更新bios"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多位先，想問點可以分到是硬件問題定Windows 10問題？<br />\n<br />\n硬件拆過Ram同Display card都係咁<br />\nMB冇爆電容<br />\nChipset有冇錯唔太明白，想問係點睇？<br />\nMB舊電是果粒扁電？<br />\n<br />\n更新Bios都有想過，不過會唔會關Windows事？<br />\n<br />\n另外HDD都會影響突然關機？<br />\n<br />\n唔該師兄"},{"pid":"a1a48f3aa0aff106c19b2c05aa14ba7c610726a7","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9af0d3471d8992428d2b50e403e9572149cebbd","tid":1989181,"uid":99861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:37:21.000Z","msg":"似死火牛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"有想過是死火牛，但用左1年多少少，平均1日用得2小時左右都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1698d45da5d837f3bf30afc55ffc39e194fbaf","tid":1989181,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09b445953aec4fc4f44241ed3be4ca157f2e017","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e5bcf75b18712d2f943aa3a0a5ec724e216eb3","tid":1989181,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇吓硬件有沒鬆<br />\n睇吓mb 有沒爆電容<br />\n睇下chipset 有沒錯<br />\n拔左mb 舊電<br />\n更新bios"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多位先，想問點可以分到是硬件問題定Windows 10問題？<br />\n<br />\n硬件拆過Ram同Display card都係咁<br />\nMB冇爆電容<br />\nChipset有冇錯唔太明白，想問係點睇？<br />\nMB舊電是果粒扁電？<br />\n<br />\n更新Bios都有想過，不過會唔會關Windows事？<br />\n<br />\n另外HDD都會影響突然關機？<br />\n<br />\n唔該師兄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:38:54.000Z","msg":"Window 10 好少會熄機開唔番<br />\n<br />\n「Chipset 有冇斷腳」（我打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n就係果粒扁電，拔出嚟，等一等再插返<br />\n<br />\nHDD正路唔會既......<br />\n通常壞咗連window都入唔到<br />\n<br />\nSSD 裝window<br />\n可能就會無端端重開機<br />\n之後又開唔著部機<br />\n<br />\n不過你話入到bios <br />\n但window 入左3個鐘就壞<br />\n所以check埋 裝window既HDD/SSD<br />\n<br />\n但按你而家情況<br />\n最好彩係換左條電源線就沒事<br />\n最差既係底板死左/火牛死"},{"pid":"febb55e3551f5ee684b1f967f8ad64d95cb58d3b","tid":1989181,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1a48f3aa0aff106c19b2c05aa14ba7c610726a7","