g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:23:20.000Z","msg":"不是家中總制，意思是機背後的火牛「拍上拍落」個制"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:26:04.000Z","msg":"火牛<br />\n咩牌子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:33:20.000Z","msg":"火牛：Cooler Master<br />\nMB: ASUS"},{"pid":"24f9b3ef16000420f01e9035dc5607ddc0f1162d","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:42:53.000Z","msg":"火牛：Cooler Master MWE GOLD 650 full modular<br />\nMB：ASUS STRIX B450F<br />\nCPU: AMD 2600X<br />\nGPU: ASUS STRIX-GTX1060-DC206G 6GB OC<br />\n256GB PCIE NVMe SSD(Windows)<br />\n1T HD"},{"pid":"6a652e921207deaeca289247a5405d96edeb244b","tid":1989181,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24f9b3ef16000420f01e9035dc5607ddc0f1162d","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:42:53.000Z","msg":"火牛：Cooler Master MWE GOLD 650 full modular<br />\nMB：ASUS STRIX B450F<br />\nCPU: AMD 2600X<br />\nGPU: ASUS STRIX-GTX1060-DC206G 6GB OC<br />\n256GB PCIE NVMe SSD(Windows)<br />\n1T HD"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:46:22.000Z","msg":"換過隻HD/SSD 9成無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792344d124e12bd6c251911cd45c92115fb4f92c","tid":1989181,"uid":187811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"各位師兄，找到了突然關機原因是出自wifi PCIE卡身上，但還未找到解決方法<br />\n<br />\n我用lan線開機24小時都沒問題，一直玩都沒問題，只要一轉用wifi就立即關機（開唔返）<br />\n因為我在用wifi PCIE卡，咁我認定左是壞卡就買新的換了張舊的（不同牌子）<br />\n<br />\n換了新wifi卡都同樣出電突然關機情況。<br />\n那我以為不關卡事，認定是PCIE slot問題換了另一slot，都出現同樣突關情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我以為Lan及Wifi撞，那我把Bios上的Lan直接關上，但只要一連網都是直接關機。<br />\n<br />\n求教達人幫忙，謝謝"}]}